name: Pagoda Warrior II
overview: It's time for some Ninja-Tastic action. Your friends have been captured inside a temple. As the brave Pagoda Warrior, you must test your ninja skills against an army of an evil worshipping cult. Once you reach the roof of the temple, it is time for the final showdown against the worshipped one, an evil serpent. Can you rescue your people and put an end to the evil cult? The winner of the 2019 SEUCK competition.
